<div class="container">
  <div class="row my-5 d-flex flex-column">
    <div class="col-10 col-md-8 col-lg-6 mx-auto p-3 p-md-5 border border-dark rounded-lg shadow">
      <div class="col text-center"><h3>お問い合わせ</h3></div>
      <div class="col form-group">
        <%= form_with model: @contact, url: confirm_contact_path,
            html: { class: "needs-validation", novalidate: :novalidate }, local: true do |f| %>
        <%= f.label :name, class: 'col col-md-3 offset-md-1 mt-3' %>
        <%= f.text_field :name, class: 'col-10 col-md-7 mx-auto form-control', required: :required %>
        <div class="invalid-feedback col-11 col-md-8 mx-auto">お名前を入力して下さい</div>
        <%= f.label :email, class: 'col col-md-5 offset-md-1 mt-3' %>
        <%= f.email_field :email, class: 'col-10 col-md-7 mx-auto form-control', required: :required %>
        <div class="invalid-feedback col-11 col-md-8 mx-auto">メールアドレスを入力して下さい</div>
        <%= f.label :content, class: 'mt-3' %>
        <%= f.text_area :content,class: 'form-control', required: :required %>
        <div class="invalid-feedback col-11 col-md-8 mx-auto">内容を入力して下さい</div>
        <div class="col text-center">
          <%= f.submit '確認画面へ', class: 'btn btn-primary rounded-pill mt-3' %>
        </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-8 mt-4 mx-auto text-center">
      <p>回答するまでに数日お時間をいただく場合がございます</p>
      <p>あらかじめご了承ください</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>